  "ai_usage": "Eye-catching media/product showcase. angleStep = 360/N; each panel i: rotateY(i*step) translateZ(radius). Wrap panels in a preserve-3d stage under a perspective container and rotate the stage (auto or via prev/next that change rotation by ±step). For production add controls, keyboard support, pause, and inert/aria-hidden on non-active panels. Disable auto-spin under reduced motion.",
  "path": "effects/3d-transforms/carousel-3d.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>3D Coverflow Carousel</title>\n  <script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n  {\n    \"id\": \"carousel-3d\",\n    \"title\": \"3D Coverflow Carousel\",\n    \"summary\": \"Cards arranged on a rotating 3D cylinder, auto-spinning — the coverflow look.\",\n    \"description\": \"Panels are distributed around a Y axis with rotateY + translateZ inside a preserve-3d stage that rotates, placing items on a virtual cylinder you can spin.\",\n    \"theme\": \"3d-transforms\",\n    \"categories\": [\"3d\", \"carousel\", \"showcase\"],\n    \"tags\": [\"carousel\", \"coverflow\", \"cylinder\", \"3d\", \"rotateY\", \"gallery\"],\n    \"tech\": [\"css\", \"js\"],\n    \"era\": \"2010s\",\n    \"difficulty\": \"advanced\",\n    \"dependencies\": [],\n    \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (3D transforms).\",\n    \"performance_notes\": \"N panels each transformed once; rotating the stage is GPU-composited. Fine for ~6-12 panels.\",\n    \"accessibility_notes\": \"Decorative showcase. For a real content carousel, provide prev/next buttons, keyboard control, pause, and ensure off-screen panels are not focus-trapped (inert/aria-hidden). Stop auto-rotate under prefers-reduced-motion.\",\n    \"customization\": [\n      { \"name\": \"--radius\", \"description\": \"Cylinder radius (panel distance)\", \"default\": \"260px\" },\n      { \"name\": \"panel count\", \"description\": \"Number of panels (sets the angle step)\", \"default\": \"6\" }\n    ],\n    \"variations\": [\"Drag to spin (pointer events)\", \"Snap to nearest panel\", \"Reflective coverflow with a CSS reflection\"],\n    \"related\": [\"cube-rotate\", \"flip-card\"],\n    \"ai_usage\": \"Eye-catching media/product showcase. angleStep = 360/N; each panel i: rotateY(i*step) translateZ(radius). Wrap panels in a preserve-3d stage under a perspective container and rotate the stage (auto or via prev/next that change rotation by ±step). For production add controls, keyboard support, pause, and inert/aria-hidden on non-active panels. Disable auto-spin under reduced motion.\"\n  }\n  </script>\n  <style>\n    :root { --radius: 240px; }\n    html, body { height: 100%; margin: 0; }\n    body { display: grid; place-items: center; background: radial-gradient(circle at 50% 40%, #1a1040, #06060c); overflow: hidden; perspective: 1100px; }\n    .stage { position: relative; width: 160px; height: 220px; transform-style: preserve-3d; animation: spin 18s linear infinite; }\n    .panel {\n      position: absolute; inset: 0; border-radius: 14px; display: grid; place-items: center; color: #fff; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.4rem;\n      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.25); box-shadow: 0 14px 40px rgba(0,0,0,.5);\n      backface-visibility: hidden;\n    }\n    .p1 { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#7c5cff,#5b3ee0); transform: rotateY(0deg) translateZ(var(--radius)); }\n    .p2 { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#2dd4bf,#0ea5a5); transform: rotateY(60deg) translateZ(var(--radius)); }\n    .p3 { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#f0abfc,#c026d3); transform: rotateY(120deg) translateZ(var(--radius)); }\n    .p4 { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#fb7185,#e11d48); transform: rotateY(180deg) translateZ(var(--radius)); }\n    .p5 { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#38bdf8,#0369a1); transform: rotateY(240deg) translateZ(var(--radius)); }\n    .p6 { background: linear-gradient(135deg,#fbbf24,#d97706); transform: rotateY(300deg) translateZ(var(--radius)); }\n    @keyframes spin { to { transform: rotateY(360deg); } }\n    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) { .stage { animation: none; } }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"stage\">\n    <div class=\"panel p1\">1</div><div class=\"panel p2\">2</div><div class=\"panel p3\">3</div>\n    <div class=\"panel p4\">4</div><div class=\"panel p5\">5</div><div class=\"panel p6\">6</div>\n  </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
